                                 <locus from="95" to="97" facs="095">Fols 95–97</locus>
                                 <note>Remnants of cut folios appear visible between <locus target="#96 #97" facs="097">folss. 96, 97, </locus> and between <locus target="#97" facs="097">97</locus> and the back cover.
